casebody.data:
Lisa E. HAMILTON, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
NORTHERN IMAGING ASSOCIATES, P.C., Ryan R. Hoenicke, M.D. and Michael W. Kuhn, D.O., Defendants-Appellants. SC: 159333
COA: 345191 Supreme Court of Michigan. June 7, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendants-appellants to extend the time for filing their reply is GRANTED. The reply will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before June 20, 2019.
